    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"772537\">@Samy Avrillon</span> I forgot to share with you my PR on Beck-Chevalley condition: <br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/22340\">https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/22340</a></p>\n<p>It's WIP, everything is done except the pentagon distributivity, which is under construction.</p>",
